data.description: SELLERS OFFERING A $5K decorating allowance on their home in the Briarwood neighborhood of Great Bridge. This all brick 4 bedroom home offers formal living and dining rooms off the 2-story foyer. Lots of natural light and wood flooring throughout. The spacious family room opens to the back deck and wooded backyard. The eat-in kitchen has a center island, bay window, desk area and pantry. Upstairs the natural light and wood flooring continues into the primary bedroom which has two separate closets, an ensuite (jetted tub, separate shower, double sink vanity) down the hall are two additional bedrooms and the hall bathroom. The fourth bedroom (FROG) is more private making it a great space for a home office or rec room. Mature landscaping. Don't miss the 3D tour.
